ting": 100, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/23ba64856db043371bdbebfe435d0f18.jpg\" /><p><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/rise-ronin-ps5-game-soulslike-way-samurai-team-ninja-1851328426\">Rise of the Ronin</a> feels like a game that\u2019s already one or two generations old. Developer Team Ninja has called it their \u201c<a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.gematsu.com/2022/09/sony-interactive-entertainment-and-team-ninja-announce-action-rpg-rise-of-the-ronin-for-ps5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">most ambitious</a>\u201d title to date, but that ambition is overshadowed by lackluster graphics, outdated design concepts, and performance issues that put the game more in line with the PS4 or even the PS3\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/rise-ronin-ps5-game-review-team-ninja-soulslike-1851355751\">Read more...</a></p>"}, {"tags": [], "album": "", "artist": null, "comments": [], "dead": false, "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 100, "source_obj__id": 175, "date_published": "2024-03-21T15:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "language": "en", "page_rating_visits": 0, "bookmarked": false, "link": "https://kotaku.com/sims-movie-margot-robbie-barbie-ea-1851355482", "vote": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/ca489e290c786059ad2c8a3c60d42da1.jpg", "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Barbie\u2019s Margot Robbie Is Working On A Sims Movie", "user": null, "page_rating": 100, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/ca489e290c786059ad2c8a3c60d42da1.jpg\" /><p>The game-to-movie pipeline is seemingly in full swing, particularly after the meteoric success of Nintendo\u2019s 2023 animated comedy <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" h