, "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 100, "source_obj__id": 175, "date_published": "2024-03-21T14:00:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "language": "en", "page_rating_visits": 0, "bookmarked": false, "link": "https://kotaku.com/fortnite-lego-pieces-worlds-uefn-creative-update-1851353810", "vote": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6dfe41ab330b708c6cd1d35fb5594f97.jpg", "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Fortnite Now Lets You Make Your Own Lego Games Inside It", "user": null, "page_rating": 100, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6dfe41ab330b708c6cd1d35fb5594f97.jpg\" /><p>The partnership between <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/lego-epic-games-fortnite-metaverse-family-friendly-onli-1848762205\">Lego and Fortnite</a> is expanding even more. Epic announced at GDC that players can now create and share games within Fortnite using Lego-themed assets. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/fortnite-lego-pieces-worlds-uefn-creative-update-1851353810\">Read more...</a></p>"}, {"tags": [], "album": "", "artist": null, "comments": [], "dead": false, "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 100, "source_obj__id": 175, "date_published": "2024-03-21T13:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "language": "en", "page_rating_visits": 0, "bookmarked": false, "link": "https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-ff7-rebirth-retry-this-current-battle-1851353657", "vote": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/1b77684249eca3702796606c56ac3df3.jpg", "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "FF7 Rebirth\u2019s Confusing \u2018Retry From This Battle\u2019 Screen Explained", "user": null, "page_rating": 100, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/1b77684249eca3702796606c56ac3df3.jpg\" /><p>As an epic RPG, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-review-ps5-1851276129\">Final Fantasy VII Rebirth</a> has a <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-combat-synergy-pressured-tips-1851239582\">ton of fights</a>. Sometimes the battle doesn\u2019t go your way and it\u2019s clear you\u2019re headed towards a \u201cgame over\u201d screen. But don\u2019t worry, Rebirth has a handy feature that can reset nearly all fight sequences in the game, bringing you back to the start for a neat little redo.\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-ff7-rebirth-retry-this-current-battle-1851353657\">Read more...</a></p>"}]